          "name_loc": "Essence Distiller",
          "desc_loc": "<h1>Active: Soul Release</h1> Provides %soul_heal_amount% health regeneration when cast on allies.<br><br>Can be ground targeted to lie dormant for up to %ground_duration%s and attach to the first enemy that comes within %latch_range% radius. When on enemies, deals %soul_damage_amount% damage per second and provides True Sight over them and shares their vision with the wearer's team.<br><br>Lasts %duration% seconds.<br><br>Gains charges every time an enemy hero dies within %soul_radius% units.",
